Quickstrike:





Quickstrike laughed loudly. "Ah ain't afraid of them. Ah ain't afraid of 
nothin'!" His face was cool and his eyes were relaxed as he looked at 
KitKat. After a moment, he leaned gently against her, not enough to put her 
off balance. He low chuckle still lingered.

He looked out into the distance and saw a figure. A female figure. He 
thrusted himself to his feet and looked carefully. It was Stingtra, and from 
the looks of it, she was damaged.

"Stingtra!" he called out, with a tone of annoyance to his deep voice. He 
ran to her, bending down. "What you do now?" He pulled her up by her upper 
arm.
